    "sentences": [
        {
            "text": "Well, so I did my first",
            "start": 0.0,
            "end": 1.48
        },
        {
            "text": "brand deal.",
            "start": 1.48,
            "end": 2.06
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm sure you guys have heard",
            "start": 2.36,
            "end": 3.4
        },
        {
            "text": "the story, but for people that",
            "start": 3.4,
            "end": 4.56
        },
        {
            "text": "I know I was off for",
            "start": 4.56,
            "end": 5.86
        },
        {
            "text": "five grand for a video.",
            "start": 5.86,
            "end": 6.92
        },
        {
            "text": "But this was when I was",
            "start": 7.06,
            "end": 7.92
        },
        {
            "text": "like, 19 and there's so much",
            "start": 7.92,
            "end": 9.84
        },
        {
            "text": "money.",
            "start": 9.84,
            "end": 10.02
        },
        {
            "text": "It's like, mom, look, look, and",
            "start": 10.14,
            "end": 12.08
        },
        {
            "text": "I was like, double it and",
            "start": 12.08,
            "end": 13.72
        },
        {
            "text": "I'll walk outside and I'll give",
            "start": 13.72,
            "end": 14.54
        },
        {
            "text": "it to homeless person.",
            "start": 14.54,
            "end": 15.38
        },
        {
            "text": "And they're like, no, you won't.",
            "start": 15.62,
            "end": 16.54
        },
        {
            "text": "That's like, double it.",
            "start": 16.9,
            "end": 17.66
        },
        {
            "text": "And I was like, pacing around",
            "start": 17.76,
            "end": 18.74
        },
        {
            "text": "my neighborhood for three hours convincing",
            "start": 18.74,
            "end": 20.1
        },
        {
            "text": "this guy.",
            "start": 20.1,
            "end": 20.7
        },
        {
            "text": "Like on the phone, just double",
            "start": 21.06,
            "end": 22.08
        },
        {
            "text": "the money.",
            "start": 22.08,
            "end": 22.42
        },
        {
            "text": "I promise the video will go",
            "start": 22.82,
            "end": 23.68
        },
        {
            "text": "viral and I'll give it to",
            "start": 23.68,
            "end": 25.0
        },
        {
            "text": "homeless person.",
            "start": 25.0,
            "end": 25.34
        },
        {
            "text": "I was like, $10 ,000, it",
            "start": 25.4,
            "end": 26.5
        },
        {
            "text": "just looks better in a title.",
            "start": 26.5,
            "end": 27.32
        },
        {
            "text": "It'll give more views.",
            "start": 27.5,
            "end": 28.06
        },
        {
            "text": "I promise you your app will",
            "start": 28.3,
            "end": 29.52
        },
        {
            "text": "do better.",
            "start": 29.52,
            "end": 29.88
        },
        {
            "text": "And I end up getting $10",
            "start": 29.88,
            "end": 31.54
        },
        {
            "text": ",000 and then gave it away",
            "start": 31.54,
            "end": 32.76
        },
        {
            "text": "in my mom's like, oh, it's",
            "start": 32.76,
            "end": 33.74
        },
        {
            "text": "just give like $8 ,000.",
            "start": 33.74,
            "end": 34.92
        },
        {
            "text": "$9 ,000.",
            "start": 35.42,
            "end": 36.0
        },
        {
            "text": "I all $10 ,000.",
            "start": 36.06,
            "end": 37.24
        },
